    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You hold forth a holy symbol or a cultural icon associated with the dead, then call forth spirits to protect you. They flit around you, striking your enemies at your direction and harrying their movement.</em></p><p>This spell targets all creatures of your choice and ignores &amp;reference[cover].</p><p><strong>Wisdom Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong><span data-text=\"true\"><strong> </strong>Targets take </span>[[/damage 3d8 radiant]]\u00a0damage*<span data-text=\"true\">.</span></p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong>Area Hazard:</strong> The area within 15 ft. of you is difficult terrain for hostile creatures.</span></p></li><li><p><strong>Concentration</strong>:\u00a0Once on each\u00a0subsequent turn, you can make the spirits target all creatures within 15 ft. of you again.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting</strong><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">: Increase damage by</span> 1d8<span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"> for each spell level above 3rd.</span></p>",
            "chat": "<p>This spell targets all creatures of your choice and ignores &amp;reference[cover].</p><p><strong>Note: This spell will add @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.aM74ghPolSDXnish]{Spirit Guardians [Damage]} to your spellbook at the top, which can be used to deal damage once per turn.</strong></p><p><strong>Wisdom Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong><span data-text=\"true\"><strong> </strong>Targets take </span>[[/damage 3d8 radiant]]\u00a0damage*<span data-text=\"true\">.</span></p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong>Area Hazard:</strong> The area within 15 ft. of you is difficult terrain for hostile creatures.</span></p></li><li><p><strong>Concentration</strong>:\u00a0Once on each\u00a0subsequent turn, you can make the spirits target all creatures within 15 ft. of you again.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting</strong><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">: Increase damage by</span> 1d8<span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"> for each spell level above 3rd.</span></p>"
        },
